Twitch VOD Cutter

This tool only works with the new VOD format (/v/1234567). It gives you the minimum number of files you need to download to get a specified section of a VOD. You can then use a tool such as ffmpeg to join the parts and convert it to a better format.
The cut is not precise and may be off by up to 4 seconds at either end.

Example: http://www.twitch.tv/user/v/1234567 or 1234567
